    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In nomine domini Dei salbatori nostri Ihesu Christi. Concessimus nos vir
                        gloriosissimus <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/327"
                            >Gisolfus</persName> divina providentia langobardorum gentis <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, pro amore omnipotentis dei et salute
                        anime nostre, <rs key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs> domne <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Principissa" ref="#people/3408"
                            >Gaitelgrime</persName> dilecte matrix nostre tibi <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/4480">Iohanni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> patri nostro et in tuo <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>, que a nobo fundamento intus hec civitatem Salernitanam
                        fundasti, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Forests #Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >terras pertinentes sacri nostri palatii</rs>, que est hiscla <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Forests #Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#places/4766">ubi Due flumina dicitur</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Actio">acto</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/3441" key="#Geographic_regions"
                            >Lucaniano</placeName>, in qua <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Churches/religious_bodies #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3727">Sancte Dei genetrici virginis
                            Marie</orgName> sita est cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">aquis</rs>, et aquarum
                        usibus per circuitum ipsius ecclesie, idest ex omnibus partibus miliaria
                        quattuor, cum finis et viis, et cum omnia infra se habentibus; in ea
                        ratione, ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum, ea que
                        prelegitur, tu nominatus Iohannes abba, tuisque successoribus et pars vestri
                        monasterii securo nomine habere et possidere baleatis, et omnia exinde
                        faciatis quod volueritis, et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, comitibus,
                        castaldeis, vel a quibuscumque agentibus, habeatis exinde aliqua
                        requisitione, set perpetuis temporibus securiter hanc firmiter eos habeatis.
                        quod vero preceptum concessionis ex iussione suprascripte potestatis (+)
                        scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary" ref="#people/4129">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName ref="#places/84"
                            key="#Cities">Salerno</placeName> palatio de anno octabo decimo, MENSE
                        NOBEMBER NONA INDICTIO. </ab>
